      "text": "\tThe 2026 FIFA World Cup is one of the most important sporting events in the world. Millions of people from different countries watch the tournament, support their favorite teams, and celebrate football together. The 2026 World Cup is especially historic because it is being hosted by three countries: the United States, Canada, and Mexico. This is the first FIFA World Cup to be shared by three host nations and the first to include 48 national teams. Because the tournament is so large and attracts worldwide attention, it also becomes connected with politics. One of the most discussed political figures during the tournament is United States President Donald Trump, whose government has an important role in helping organize the event.",
